The authoritative SOURCE_LOCATIONS file is generated during image build from
the bundled APK metadata and copied into:

  /usr/share/licenses/pcinfo-classic/SOURCE_LOCATIONS

Generated columns:
  package
  version
  origin
  repo
  license
  package_page
  apkbuild_tree

The generated file points to:
  - the Alpine package metadata page for the exact package name, and
  - the Alpine aports tree location for the package origin on 3.21-stable.

For packages modified locally after extraction, see:

  PATCHES/kexec-tools-binary-adjustment.txt
